parameters:
[Duncan] I was told not to lend that room to anyone else without
permission because it might be rented to someone else...

[Duncan] Indeed, the one who has reserved that room is not Anastasia-
sama, but the Academy...

[Duncan] As for me, I was extremely disappointed, thinking that I had
to lend it to someone else.

[Duncan] Oh, but I'm glad. Anastasia-sama will be using it again today,
right?
[Anastasia] U-Um, I have a favor to ask...
[Anastasia] ...Is there any way... you could let me stay...?

[Duncan] Hmm, personally, I would be very welcoming if it were
Anastasia-sama...

[Duncan] Since we have a reservation at the Academy, if by any chance
someone else were to come, it would be troublesome, so umm... I
guess... I can't just...
[Anastasia] I... I will... do something for you...
[Duncan] U-um... your voice is so soft... Did I... misunderstand...?
[Duncan] C-Can I... ask you one more time?
[Anastasia] I-I will... p-provide... s-some... s-sensual service...
[Anastasia] I want you to secretly let me stay at the Academy...
[Duncan] I-Is that true?! Really... you will... do that for me?!

[Anastasia] I-I will... p-provide... s-sensual service... with my
mouth...
[Anastasia] Please, let me stay at the Academy...

[Duncan] If I could receive that from Anastasia-sama... hehehe, with
your mouth... gufufu... I would gladly keep it a secret from the
Academy.
[Anastasia] W-Well then... p-please... take care of me.
